</ul></nav></section><section class="front-matter"><div class="ameta p font-secondary font-xs">
<hgroup><h1>Data Consult Service: Can we use observational data to address immediate clinical needs?</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Ostropolets%20A"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Anna Ostropolets</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
<h3><span class="name western">Anna Ostropolets</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Department of Biomedical Informatics, Columbia University Medical Center, New York, New York, USA</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Ostropolets%20A"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Anna Ostropolets</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1,</sup><sup>✉</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Zachariah%20P"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id2"><span class="name western">Philip Zachariah</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id2">
<h3><span class="name western">Philip Zachariah</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Department of Biomedical Informatics, Columbia University Medical Center, New York, New York, USA</div>
<div class="p">
<sup>2</sup>NewYork-Presbyterian Hospital, New York, New York, USA</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Zachariah%20P"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Philip Zachariah</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1,</sup><sup>2</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Ryan%20P"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id3"><span class="name western">Patrick Ryan</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id3">
<h3><span class="name western">Patrick Ryan</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Department of Biomedical Informatics, Columbia University Medical Center, New York, New York, USA</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Ryan%20P"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Patrick Ryan</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Chen%20R"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id4"><span class="name western">Ruijun Chen</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id4">
<h3><span class="name western">Ruijun Chen</span></h3>
<div class="p">
